{"tid":1529051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場逃亡之旅","createTime":"2019-09-01T16:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T16:19:26.000Z","uid":235801,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6f4e361837d31c5a513b06dd34e996e5c1cc6e61","tid":1529051,"uid":235801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:00:19.000Z","msg":"屌，cls攰到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，由機場行到東涌再去到青馬廣場，我都唔知嗰度行咗幾多K，成程都勁撚驚險，中途成日要凝住會有狗車突然間停低捉人，到咗青馬跟住我就求其上咗架出巿區嘅巴士。<br />\n<br />\n原本係搭去美孚再搭西鐵翻去，當我搭到錦上路，仆你個臭街原來仲未完，跟住我就收到風屯門元朗天水圍都有狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，嚇撚都我搭對頭車返美孚再轉巴士先翻到屋企。唔好屌我，慣撚咗搭鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想講嘅係就算今次幾咁驚險，我下次都係唔會因為驚而唔出嚟，期待你班黑警比人清算嘅一日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"7e4051d851782eb26e222e18364d3f9bf374c908","tid":1529051,"uid":1102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"辛苦你la 巴打，好好休息下"},{"pid":"9da21205898bf7e9b0c4f0ff0da7877fe7678c0a","tid":1529051,"uid":38784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:02:21.000Z","msg":"好好休息"},{"pid":"215a1a70f072ea5ec80864d0757c145f84bff887","tid":1529051,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:02:39.000Z","msg":"辛苦哂,安全最緊要"},{"pid":"45ec37b57f47f11425df5e24c4169eaea4b8714c","tid":1529051,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite